        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Lesson 5 • Talking about company strategy</b>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "keyword": "Andy and Laura work for Saltonica, a maker of cell phones. Sales have been slow lately, so Andy is recommending the company adopt a new strategy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> My team has come up with a new strategy. We can't continue being"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "fast followers",
              "word": "fast followers"
            },
            {
              "enText": ". We need to start developing our own"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "cutting-edge",
              "word": "cutting-edge"
            },
            {
              "enText": "technologies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> Why? We've been"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "fast followers",
              "word": "fast followers"
            },
            {
              "enText": "for the past ten years."
            },
            {
              "keyword": "Why mess with success?",
              "word": "Why mess with success?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> Success?"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "get with the program",
              "word": "Get with the program"
            },
            {
              "enText": ". Our sales are way down. Our "
            },
            {
              "keyword": "cash cow",
              "word": "cash cow"
            },
            {
              "enText": ", the Model 8B, only sold 900 units last month!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> I can understand why. That phone's a relic.* It's been around for over three years. What about our new phones?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> Our latest model cell phone was a"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "real dog",
              "word": "real dog"
            },
            {
              "enText": "! It sold only 20 percent of our sales forecast."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> Any idea why?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> Product life cycles are much shorter now than before. New technologies are developed at a much faster rate."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> So what are we supposed to do?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> We need to become much more innovative as a company. Instead of producing"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "me-too products",
              "word": "me-too products"
            },
            {
              "enText": ", we need to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "leapfrog one's competitors",
              "word": "leapfrog our competitors"
            },
            {
              "enText": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> How do we do that?"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b>"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "for starters",
              "word": "For starters"
            },
            {
              "enText": ", we need to"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "beef up",
              "word": "beef up "
            },
            {
              "enText": "our R&D* department. We need to develop differentiated products which we can sell"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "at a premium",
              "word": "at a premium"
            },
            {
              "enText": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Laura:</b> As a next step, let's"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "get buy-in",
              "word": "get buy-in"
            },
            {
              "enText": "from our marketing and sales directors."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "paragraphs": [
            {
              "enText": "<b>Andy:</b> Right. We should get everyone"
            },
            {
              "keyword": "on the same page",
              "word": " on the same page"
            },
            {
              "enText": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
